                        Your first consultation will include a comprehensive style assessment, body shape analysis, 
                        color analysis, and discussion of your lifestyle and style goals. We'll create a personalized 
                        action plan to help you achieve your desired look.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md">
                <button class="faq-question w-full text-left p-6 focus:outline-none" onclick="toggleFAQ(this)">
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">How long does a typical consultation last?</h3>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down transition-transform"></i>
